Product name: 4, Personalized Groomsmen Gift, Engraved Flask Set, Stainless Steel Flask, Personalized Best Man Gift, 4 Flask Sets
Description:
A perfect gift for your groomsmen on your wedding day, our personalized flask sets will help you celebrate in style. Designed to carry liquor, the 6 ounce black, powder coated flask and shot (cups) are made of stainless steel. Our state-of-the-art laser engraves the powder coating resulting in a durable, beautiful silver engraving, which shines in any light. 
Our listing is for FOUR personalized flask sets. Packed in a sturdy black gift box, each set includes; one flask, four stainless steel cups and one funnel, and any one of the above flask engraving designs.
SIZE: 
The flask measures approximately 3-1/2" wide x 4" tall, and each shot cup holds 1 ounce of liquor.
PERSONALIZATION:
The front side of each flask will be personalized with your choice of an engraving design (see the above photos and drop-down menu). If you'd like a custom design, contact us via ‘Etsy conversations' to specify the details for the text or image you'd like. 
ORDERING: 
Select the engraving design and cups from the drop-down menus and click the "add to cart" button, specify ALL engraving instructions in the note box under "notes to Engravingpro" on the add to cart page. Include the following information if applicable:
1) Name;
2) Title;
3) Wedding date.
Most orders are ready and shipped within 5 business days after receiving payment. Most flask sets are shipped Ground (with expected delivery of 2 to 9 days). Shipping upgrades are offered at checkout.

Product name: Bachelorette Party Veil, Hen Party Veil, Bridal Shower Veil - White Tulle Veil with Bow
Description:
Perfect accessory for your favorite bride-to-be for her bachelorette party or bridal shower!
This party veil has six layers of soft bridal illusion tulle gathered and clean finished at the top with a ribbon.
The top is finished with a ribbon bow in your choice of colors.  All bows are made from grosgrain ribbon except the Gold Glitter, Iridescent, Pink Glitter and Silver Glitter which are made from a sparkly glitter ribbon.
Choose between a French barrette or a clear plastic hair comb.
Veil measures 18" (45.5 cm) long.
Current make time is 3-5 business days plus shipping time. Standard shipping within the United States is USPS First Class and  generally takes 2-5 business days (but does not have a guaranteed delivery date and can take longer). Standard international shipping can take anywhere from 10 days to 4 weeks. There are faster shipping options available - you'll need to add the item to your cart and put in your zip or country to see all shipping options and prices.
***If you need the veil by a certain date, PLEASE add a note to your order with your need-by-date!***
Looking for a different color tulle or bow?  Click "Request a custom order" and let us know what you  need!
When you receive it, your veil will be a bit wrinkled from shipping. Hang it up to relax the fabric and then if necessary, steam with a fabric steamer or steam iron - hold iron 2” away from fabric - keeping heat away from the bow.  Or easier yet, hang it in the bathroom while running a hot shower.
